      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Historique\n- 1989-1991 - 1ere version - Guido van Rossum\n- 2001 - Python Software Foundation - python.org\n        Python 2.1+ opensource\n- 2009 - version 3.0 (réecriture complète)\n            version 2.7 \n- 2020 - EOL de python 2.7\n- 2025 - version 3.14\n\nAvantages\n- multi plateforme : Windows, Linux, Mac, ...\n- syntaxe simple\n- communauté importante : https://pypi.org/\n    * Web\n    * Data - Calcul scientifique - IA\n    * GIS\n    * OS Linux\n\nEnvironnement de programmation\n- VSCode\n- PyCharm\n- Spyder\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Historique\n- 1989-1991 - 1ere version - Guido van Rossum\n- 2001 - Python Software Foundation - python.org\n        Python 2.1+ opensource\n- 2009 - version 3.0 (réecriture complète)\n            version 2.7 \n- 2020 - EOL de python 2.7\n- 2025 - version 3.14\n\nAvantages\n- multi plateforme : Windows, Linux, Mac, ...\n- syntaxe simple\n- communauté importante : https://pypi.org/\n    * Web\n    * Data - Calcul scientifique - IA\n    * GIS\n    * OS Linux\n\nEnvironnement de programmation\n- VSCode\n- PyCharm\n- Spyder\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
